templates: append Cmd when Entrypoint is a string

Per Docker semantics, Cmd provides default arguments to Entrypoint
regardless of whether Entrypoint is a string or an array. The template
previously ignored Cmd when Entrypoint was a plain string.

Fix the lxc.init.cmd template to append Cmd in all cases:
 - string Entrypoint + string Cmd
 - string Entrypoint + array Cmd

Add test coverage for these combinations.

Upstream-Status: Pending

